{"type": "article", "id": 5237, "title": "senz 雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-15T07:59:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523352415I6DiJ2BGfKqWNc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计师 Gerwin Hoogendoorn 曾有过一周内弄坏 3 把雨伞的经历，于是他为美国品牌 Opening Ceremony 设计了这把名为「senz」的雨伞。这是一把利用空气动力学原理设计的不对称雨伞，致力于解决传统雨伞在极端狂风暴雨天气里并不能起到遮风挡雨作用的缺陷，伞布上还印有 OC Logo 。Gerwin Hoogendoorn 将设计的关键锁定在伞骨位置，不规则多角的设计使得雨伞便于调整角度、减小风阻，且给人一种很酷的感觉。定价 79 美元（约合人民币 489 元），<a href=\"https://www.openingceremony.us/products.asp?menuid=2&amp;menuid2=5&amp;designerid=2177&amp;productid=131857\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335225J7TSp4YZFHsPfxV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233523PdQTKsUtI9qNacVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233523SLWuG0PxwsyCqBdj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}